$PACKAGE          n
$SUMMARY          Routines to generate random numbers
$PURPOSE
    These routines are meant to provide a simple way of generating random
    numbers.
$LIBRARY          karma
$LINKWITH         -lkarma
$END

$FUNCTION           n_gaussian
$RETURN_TYPE        double
$PARAMETER_LIST
    ()
$SUMMARY            Compute a random number with Gaussian distribution.
$PURPOSE
    This routine will compute a random number with a Gaussian
    distribution. The mean is 0.0 and the variance is 1.0
$RETURNS
    The number.
$END

$FUNCTION           n_uniform
$RETURN_TYPE        double
$PARAMETER_LIST
    ()
$SUMMARY            Compute a random number with Uniform distribution.
$PURPOSE
    This routine will compute a random number with a Uniform
    distribution. The range is from 0.0 to 1.0
$RETURNS
    The number.
$END
